content.p: Harresh Kasivisvanthan, a PhD Chemical and Environmental Engineering student, discusses his research, the Malaysian Campus lab facilities, and his future plans for a self-supported biorefinery. Tee Choun Zee is a Malaysian PhD student in Chemical and Environmental Engineering. He talks about life as a PhD student and his research. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8001
